title: Within the Ruins Complete Discography (2006-2013)
description:
This is a complete discography as of June 27th, 2013.
None of the content is my own, I've simply created an all-in-one collection of the albums I've obtained online for convenience.

Album list:
Driven By Fear (2006)
Empires (2008)
Creatures (2009)
Invade (2010)
Omen (2011)
Elite (2013)

Note:
If you'd like to request something that you know is available in stores but is difficult to find online, I'll consider purchasing, ripping, and uploading. Just leave your request in the comments below.

Bear in mind, the intention behind my uploads is to spread great music in the hopes that it will motivate people to show support (it's understandable to not want to pay for the songs, so I always recommend buying merchandise or going to shows!)
If you enjoy the music, please support the artists!
